CHANGES
============================================================================

Release 0.2.11 (2010-07-09)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * PM-only cache - missing waypoint bug.


Release 0.2.10 (2010-07-01)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * Missing cache guid bug (update GCparser).


Release 0.2.9 (2010-06-07)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * 10y cache type icon bugfix (again :)).


Release 0.2.8 (2010-06-07)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * Update GCparser to v0.4.4.

  * New plugin: elevations (download SRTM data and generate statistics).

  * Move update scripts from Pyggs class to plugins.

[Bugfixes]

  * Several typos.

  * Cache type bugfix.


Release 0.2.6 (2010-02-01)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * Prevent myFinds databse update by empty list and force myFinds databse
    update on new version of Pyggs.

  * Update GCparser to v0.4.

[Bugfixes]

  * Several typos.


Release 0.2.5 (2010-01-13)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * GS webpage design update -> GCParser update.

  * Minor fixes in colored console output.

  * Fixed PM-only cache bug.


Release 0.2.4 (2009-11-27)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * Weird GS changes in type name Unknown vs. Mystery/Puzzle.


Release 0.2.3 (2009-11-27)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * GCparser update: lessen the load on geocaching servers.

  * Change console text color on startup.

[Bugfixes]

  * Refresh version info in pyggsDir.

  * PM cache.


Release 0.2.2 (2009-11-10)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * Change of type name Unknown -> Mystery/Puzzle.


Release 0.2.1 (2009-11-08)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * GCparser events date - thanks to Ruda Hamak.


Release 0.2 (2009-09-21)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * Config file encoding problem.

  * Event and Webcam logs are now in MyFinds.

[Enhancements]

  * New version of GCparser.

  * New more intuitive setup system.

  * A lot of code cleaning:
      - a lot of minor improvements in plugin system
      - better colored output handling
      - working directory is unfortunately backwards incompatible


Release 0.1.1 (2009-09-11)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * Plugin setup script in alphabetical order.

  * Missing translations.

  * gcczMyRatingsTop10 plugin fix.


Release 0.1 (2009-09-09)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * Initial set of plugins.